"Sundar Pichai: And, Justin, on the live streaming question, you know, I already have mentioned that live stream is a big focus for us. You know, we've been at it for a while. And we've built a great, robust, and mature platform for big events. We just announced at VidCon our plans to make mobile live streaming features available within our core YouTube app on all mobile devices. You know, our stream time, live stream time, has increased 3X since the beginning of the year alone. And YouTube is the first major platform to support live content in 360 degrees. And, you know, recent examples, I'm -- even the RNC and the DNC conventions, they've been live streamed on YouTube in 360. And it's -- you know, so there's a lot of momentum there. And we are absolutely committed to the space."